platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 認識你的私人腦力教練

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Défiez votre concentration, mémoire et votre coordination.
Work your brain by challenging your focus, memory and coordination.
Exercise your mental agility—your focus, memory and coordination.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: You use all kinds of specialized equipment at the gym to keep your body in shape, but what about your brain? Peak is a comprehensive collection of exercises designed to hone your memory, sharpen your problem-solving skills, enhance your mental agility, and more. Daily workouts covering up to five areas of focus will leave your mind feeling limber, and you can track your results over time and even compare them to other Peak users in your age group. Best of all, mental gymnastics don’t cause painful brain-sprains.
